 

Steps of Deletion Process of Students Data

Go to Profile Screen, User can see "Delete Profile" Button

When the user clicks the "Delete Profile" button, initiate the deletion process.
This triggers the confirmation dialog, asking the user to confirm the action.

Prompt the user with a dialog box that asks, “Are you sure you want to delete your profile? This action cannot be undone.”
This confirmation helps prevent accidental deletion.

Sign Out the User

After both the profile picture and inforamtion record are deleted, log the user out.

Redirect to Login Screen

Redirect the user to the login screen to finalize the logout and deletion process.
